Closing Ceremony of the Agricultural Project Workshop Series
1  March,  2024
The closing ceremony for the series of workshops of the Agricultural Project was held as part of the "My Project" initiative to honor the supporting entity, Plaza Hollandi, and the participants in the workshops. The ceremony was also attended by the Executive Director of the Ajeel Educational Center, Dr. Abu Bakr Musa Abdullah.
